uk.ac.ebi.pride.utilities.data.core

Class ParamGroup

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ebi.pride.utilities.data.core.ParamGroup
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, MassSpecObject
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BinaryDataArray, FragmentIon, Gel, IdentifiableParamGroup, InstrumentComponent, InstrumentConfiguration, MassTable, ProcessingMethod, Scan, ScanList, ScanSetting

    public class ParamGroup
extends Object
implements MassSpecObject
    ParamGroup is a container for CvParams and UserParams. This class is included in neither mzML nor PRIDE xml definition. In theory, both cv params and user params can be null. This container is extended for some several classes that contain cvParameters as information.

    Author:
    ypriverol, rwang Date: 25-Jan-2010 Time: 15:58:01
